ous demise? then read on.</font><BR></td></tr><TR><TD valign="top"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/lotr/gfx/star2.gif" width="19" height="21" border="0" align="absmiddle"></td><td><font face="Papy, Times, serif" class="h2font"><A HREF="/lotr/articles/articles.php?id=3035&view=2">So.....you're a minion, huh?</A></Font><BR><font face="  Times, Times New Roman, serif" class="bfont">A quick look at each of the shadow races in LOTR, touching on their strengths and weaknesses, and what sets them apart from each other.</font><BR></td></tr></table> 
